Name: A Very Non-Obvious Winter Holiday Playlist
Description: We can hear an endless stream of the same boring Christmas songs if we turn on the radio. Let's do better and create a non-obvious winter holiday playlist.

Name: Secret santa!
Description:
Draw a name: https://drawnames.app/t/-0qCpw0

Now submit a song for that person:
submit something you think they’ll like based on what you’ve seen in music league. Submitting a song by a band you’ve already seen them submit is too boring/obvious.

Name: "what is the most rockingest rock song of all of rock time?"
this song is my resolution
Description:
Happy New Year!

Both deadly serious and jokey answers are accepted, but please do explain in the comments.

Name: Something that doesn’t sound like any previous submission
Description:
It's a new year, time for new sounds!

Sam's Rules: By "any previous submission" it really just means Season 11 onwards (most current players have been around for most of the last 4 seasons). It's more of a "spirit rather than the letter of the law" kind of prompt anyway,  so don't feel you have to research 10 seasons you weren't around for.

Name: wait.. what did you think that song was about?!
Description:
You’d been listening to this for years... and it turns out you had no idea what it was about.

Tell us in the comments what you thought it was about and what it's actually about.

Name: Musical equivalent of "a joke that needs to be explained"
Description: a song that needs a supporting comment to explain how clever it is

Name: some wholesome content
Description: time for the opposite: give us a wholesome fav of urs

Name: You probably haven’t heard of them
Description: Artists with less than 10k monthly listeners.
